{"prompt": "Generate a website for a professional law firm. The website should be modern and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Legal</title>\n    <style>\n        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;700&family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&display=swap');\n\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0d47a1;\n            --secondary-color: #90caf9;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --header-footer-bg: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            margin: 5px 0 0;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            padding: 15px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 0;\n            z-index: 1000;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 20px;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 100px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            opacity: 0.2;\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        .hero-content {\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin: 0 0 20px;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: white;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 35px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            border: 2px solid white;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            border-color: white;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 80px 0;\n        }\n\n        section h3 {\n            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 50px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);\n        }\n\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            display: block;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h4 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .about-content {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .about-text {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n\n        .about-image {\n            flex: 1;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .about-image img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n        }\n\n        .contact-form {\n            background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\n            padding: 50px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form input,\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 22px);\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form textarea {\n            min-height: 150px;\n            resize: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 15px 35px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        .social-icons {\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .social-icons a {\n            color: white;\n            margin: 0 10px;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .social-icons a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        /* Font Awesome for icons - you'd need to include this library */\n        .fas {\n            font-family: 'Font Awesome 5 Free';\n            font-weight: 900;\n        }\n    </style>\n    <!-- You would typically link to Font Awesome CDN here -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Apex Legal</h1>\n            <p>Dedicated to Justice and Excellence</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <a href=\"#services\">Services</a>\n            <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n            <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container hero-content\">\n            <h2>Your Trusted Advocates</h2>\n            <p>Providing expert legal counsel and representation with integrity and precision.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Schedule a Consultation</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Our Practice Areas</h3>\n            <div class=\"services-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-gavel\"></i>\n                    <h4>Corporate Law</h4>\n                    <p>Navigating complex business transactions, mergers, and acquisitions with strategic expertise.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-user-shield\"></i>\n                    <h4>Litigation</h4>\n                    <p>Aggressive and meticulous representation in all forms of dispute resolution.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-home\"></i>\n                    <h4>Real Estate Law</h4>\n                    <p>Ensuring smooth property transactions and resolving disputes.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-file-contract\"></i>\n                    <h4>Contract Law</h4>\n                    <p>Drafting, reviewing, and enforcing agreements to protect your interests.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" style=\"background-color: var(--header-footer-bg);\">\n        <div class=\"container about-content\">\n            <div class=\"about-text\">\n                <h3>About Apex Legal</h3>\n                <p>Founded on principles of integrity, diligence, and client advocacy, Apex Legal is a premier law firm committed to delivering exceptional legal services. Our team of seasoned attorneys brings a wealth of experience and a deep understanding of the law to every case. We pride ourselves on building strong, lasting relationships with our clients by offering personalized attention and strategic, effective solutions.</p>\n                <p>We believe in clear communication, transparent processes, and achieving the best possible outcomes for those we represent.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"about-image\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/0d47a1/ffffff?text=Law+Firm+Image\" alt=\"Law Firm Building\">\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Get In Touch</h3>\n            <div class=\"contact-form\">\n                <form id=\"contactForm\">\n                    <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                    <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                    <input type=\"tel\" name=\"phone\" placeholder=\"Your Phone Number\">\n                    <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                    <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n                </form>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Legal. All Rights Reserved.</p>\n            <div class=\"social-icons\">\n                <a href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-facebook-f\"></i></a>\n                <a href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-twitter\"></i></a>\n                <a href=\"#\"><i class=\"fab fa-linkedin-in\"></i></a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {\n            event.preventDefault();\n            // In a real application, you would send this data to a server\n            alert('Thank you for your message! We will be in touch soon.');\n            this.reset();\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}